006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.constraint;
007
008import java.util.List;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011
012/**
013 * A common interface used for constraints oriented around key-based indexes.
014 */
015public interface IKeyConstraint extends IConfigurableMessageConstraint {
016  /**
017   * Retrieve the list of keys to use in creating and looking up an entry in a
018   * given index.
019   *
020   * @return one or more keys
021   */
022  @NonNull
023  List<? extends IKeyField> getKeyFields();
024}
